NHUNGAMIRO YE UPENYU

0:00:03.520,0:00:07.900
Zvawave kuzoona zvinoratidza kuratidzwa kwakanakisa kwe chishamiso chimwe chetecho

0:00:07.900,0:00:11.740
sechakaitika muupenyu hwe murume pa musuwowe temberi wainzi Rakanaka muna Mabasa 3.

0:00:11.740,0:00:15.800
Tarisa uone pachezvako uye upe mbiri kuna Mwari!

0:00:17.880,0:00:19.520
O, tarisa!

0:00:19.520,0:00:22.080
Chokwadi zvinosiririsa kuona!

0:00:22.080,0:00:26.580
Uye anofanira kunge aine nyaya inosuwisa pamusoro pekutambura kwake,

0:00:26.580,0:00:29.860
nokuda kwe kuremara kwake!

0:00:29.860,0:00:34.500
Murume murombo akaremara uyu anoshandisa maoko nemakumbo

0:00:34.500,0:00:37.140
kuti azvikwezve achienda ne pasi,

0:00:37.140,0:00:42.200
nekusa kwanisa kutenga wiricheya kana chero imwe nzira ye kuti afambe.

0:00:42.200,0:00:47.960
Murume uyu anga akaremara kwemakore gumi apfuura.

0:00:47.960,0:00:51.840
Nemisodzi yekuyaura ichiyerera pamatama ake,

0:00:51.840,0:00:57.180
chiso chake chiratidzo chekupererwa zvachose.

0:00:57.180,0:01:01.380
Anochema nokuti haana kuremara chete,

0:01:01.380,0:01:05.140
asi kuti arikurarama muurombo hwakanyanya.

0:01:05.140,0:01:08.020
Urombo hwai uhwu!

0:01:08.020,0:01:12.980
Ungafungidzira kuti zvingava zvakaita sei kukambaira ne maoko ako ne tsoka dzako.

0:01:12.980,0:01:16.100
se nzira yako yega yekuti ubve pa nzvimbo imwe kuenda kune imwe nzvimbo.

0:01:16.100,0:01:17.680
Zita rangu ndi Ajayi Ogunleye

0:01:17.680,0:01:20.920
Dambudziko randiudza pa SCOAN nderekuti ndakaremara

0:01:20.920,0:01:22.480
Handigoni kufamba.

0:01:22.480,0:01:27.660
Handina mubatsiri kunze kwekunge Mwari atumira munhu kuzondiropafadza.

0:01:27.660,0:01:32.440
Pandinenge ndakagara panze ndichipemha, ndinodana chero we chidiki anenge achipfuura

0:01:32.440,0:01:35.020
kuti andibatsire nekundicherera mvura yekugeza

0:01:35.020,0:01:38.620
Dzimwe nguva, apo ndinopa vanhu mari ne ndiro kuti vanditengere zvokudya

0:01:38.620,0:01:40.020
vanotiza nayo.

0:01:40.020,0:01:43.800
Ndaneta nazvo; ndicho chikonzero ndabva ikoko ndichiuya pano.

0:01:43.800,0:01:45.500
Ndinoziva kuti kuuya pano, ndinoporeswa.

0:01:45.500,0:01:50.620
Kudzokera kumba ndisina kuporeswa, zviri nani kuti ndife hangu.

0:01:51.660,0:01:55.400
Achitsvaka kunyange zvinhu zvinokosha,

0:01:55.400,0:01:58.240
aripano kuti asangane ne mu Porofita T.B. Joshua

0:01:58.240,0:02:04.900
kuti aone nezvinodiwa zvake maererano ne mari, zvokudya, pokugara, zvokupfeka,

0:02:04.900,0:02:08.000
kana wiricheya kubatsira mafambiro ake.

0:02:08.000,0:02:15.540
Sekupa kwange kuchiita mu Porofita T.B. Joshua vamwe vari mumamiriro ezvinhu akafanana naye.

0:02:15.540,0:02:17.880
Arikutsvaga sirivha ne goridhe.

0:02:17.880,0:02:20.620
Asi chii chakakosha kwaari icho anoda?

0:02:20.620,0:02:23.840
I sirivha ne goridhe here kana kuti kuporeswa?

0:02:25.780,0:02:27.760
Tarisa maoko ake

0:02:27.760,0:02:31.880
ane mhoni, kukwasharara  pamwe ne tsvina

0:02:31.880,0:02:36.460
ndiwo maoko ayo anoshandisa kuzvikwezva pasi

0:02:36.460,0:02:39.260
Anopinza ruoko mukati me hembe yake yakabvaruka.

0:02:39.260,0:02:44.840
uye anobudisa chisaga chakatindivara ne tsvina icho chakasungirirwa mumutsipa make.

0:02:44.840,0:02:48.380
Kubva mukati me saga, anobudisa bhegi rechikweshe

0:02:48.380,0:02:51.400
rine mari yose yaainayo,

0:02:51.400,0:02:54.540
isingakanwe kunyangwe kudya kunogutsa.

0:02:54.540,0:02:56.720
Akasendamira kune rimwe divi,

0:02:56.720,0:03:01.040
anoratidza chi mutefetefe chakabvaruka icho anoshandisa se kusheni

0:03:01.040,0:03:07.300
kuitira kuti mafambiro ake arege kunyanya kumurwadza apo anenge achizvikwezva

0:03:07.300,0:03:14.180
Chimutefete chakakwasharara ndicho chega chaainacho kuzvidzivirira kubva kupasi pakaoma, ne ku matombo,

0:03:14.180,0:03:21.680
ma bhotoro akapwanyika, nezvimwewo zvinobaya zvaanosangana nazvo nguva dzese munzira yake.

0:03:23.540,0:03:30.560
Anoenda kuno mirira mu Porofita T.B. Joshua pa gedhi re SCOAN

0:03:30.560,0:03:36.660
kuti akumbire mari nerubatsiro sezvakaita murume pamusuo Rakanaka mubhuku re Mabasa chitsauko 3

0:03:36.660,0:03:39.340
uyo akakumbira sirivha ne goridhe

0:03:39.340,0:03:44.520
Asi muPostori Petro, kuburikidza ne simba re Mweya Mutsvene, akamupa chimwe chinhu

0:03:44.520,0:03:47.140
chakadarika sirivha ne goridhe

0:03:47.140,0:03:51.200
chimwe chinhu chinoita kuti mari ishomeke.

0:03:51.200,0:03:54.200
Akapiwa zvinokosha izvo anoda.

0:03:54.200,0:03:57.400
Sezvakaita murume wepasuo Rakanaka,

0:03:57.400,0:04:03.320
murume uyu akagara pagedhi repa SCOAN

0:04:03.320,0:04:06.200
Chii chakakosha mu upenyu hwake?

0:04:06.200,0:04:07.680
wiricheya?

0:04:07.680,0:04:09.060
imba?

0:04:09.060,0:04:10.200
chekudya?

0:04:10.200,0:04:11.620
shamwari?

0:04:11.620,0:04:13.320
Imari here?

0:04:13.320,0:04:16.100
kana chimwe chinhu chakapfuura izvozvo?

0:04:16.100,0:04:21.480
Tinonamata kuti nyaya yake ifanane ne zvakaitika ku murume wepasuo Rakanaka.

0:04:21.480,0:04:26.600
