0:04:41.240,0:04:46.120
Munhu wa Mwari, mu Porofita T.B. Joshua, arimunzira kuenda kugedhi.

0:04:46.120,0:04:49.180
Anoona murume uya achibva ananga kwaari.

0:04:49.180,0:04:53.560
