0:04:58.060,0:05:00.280
Mwari anogona kushandisa chero chinhu kuporesa

0:05:00.280,0:05:05.480
Muchiitiko chino, Anoshandisa shangu dze muPorofita T.B. Joshua senzvimbo yekubatana naye

0:05:05.480,0:05:07.880
