0:05:21.700,0:05:26.020
Muporofita T.B. Joshua anobva, achiziva kuti zvatoitwa

0:05:26.020,0:05:34.540
Sezvaanogaro taura achiti,"Handini mu poresi, ndinoziva muporesi, Zita rake ndi Jesu Kristu."

0:05:34.540,0:05:37.540
Jesu aporesa murume uyu.

0:05:37.540,0:05:39.600
Ichi chishamiso

0:05:39.600,0:05:43.300
Nhengo dzakaona zvichiitika dzinouya pamberi

0:05:43.300,0:05:46.160
